---
import "../../styles/global.css";
---

<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <link rel="icon" href="/logo-t.png" />
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://asanotakuya.com/works/dd-sketch-c" />

  <title>DD Sketch C | Takuya Asano</title>
  <meta
    name="description"
    content="DD Sketch C by Takuya Asano. The third volume in a three-part return to earlier recordings from the DD series."
  />

  <meta property="og:title" content="DD Sketch C | Takuya Asano" />
  <meta
    property="og:description"
    content="DD Sketch C by Takuya Asano. The third volume in a three-part return to earlier recordings from the DD series."
  />
  <meta property="og:image" content="https://asanotakuya.com/images/ddsketch_c.jpg" />
  <meta property="og:type" content="article" />
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://asanotakuya.com/works/dd-sketch-c" />

  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
  <meta name="twitter:title" content="DD Sketch C | Takuya Asano" />
  <meta
    name="twitter:description"
    content="DD Sketch C by Takuya Asano. The third volume in a three-part return to earlier recordings from the DD series."
  />
  <meta name="twitter:image" content="https://asanotakuya.com/images/ddsketch_c.jpg" />
</head>

<body>
  <header class="site-header">
    <div class="container header-inner">
      <a href="/" class="site-title">Takuya Asano</a>
      <nav class="nav">
        <a href="/works">Works</a>
        <a href="/news">News</a>
        <a href="/about">About</a>
        <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <p class="work-meta fade-in">2025 · Album</p>
      <h1 class="page-title fade-in">DD Sketch C</h1>

      <p class="fade-in">
        The third volume in a three-part return to the DD series.
      </p>

      <div class="work-detail-image fade-in">
        <img src="/images/ddsketch_c.jpg" alt="DD Sketch C artwork" />
      </div>

      <div class="fade-in" style="margin-top: 72px;">
        <p>
          <em>DD Sketch C</em> gathers DD32 to DD42 from the ongoing DD improvisation series.
        </p>

        <p>
          These recordings were made after the first album <em>DD</em>, and before they had been assembled into a broader sequence of their own.
        </p>

        <p>
          With this third volume, the arc of <em>DD Sketch</em> comes into view.<br />
          Together, A, B, and C form a set of small studies — each separate, yet all part of one longer movement.
        </p>

        <p>
          They can be heard like pages turned slowly, carrying different temperatures, spaces, and traces of time.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="fade-in" style="margin-top: 56px;">
        <p>
          The third volume of <em>DD Sketch</em>, gathering DD32 to DD42 and completing the arc of the series.<br />
          Released in 2025.
        </p>

        <p lang="ja">
          DDシリーズのうち、DD32からDD42を収めた作品集。<br />
          3部作の最後の巻として、時間や空気の異なるスケッチがひとつの流れとして結ばれています。
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="fade-in" style="margin-top: 72px;">
        <a
          href="https://open.spotify.com/intl-ja/album/2VR96Cjk2A9eGQwG6y2S36?si=so8mn6EoR7qF1WnX_Agw0w"
          class="text-link"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          Listen
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="fade-in" style="margin-top: 80px;">
        <a href="/works" class="text-link">Back to Works</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <script is:inline>
    const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
      entries.forEach((entry) => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          entry.target.classList.add("is-visible");
        }
      });
    }, { threshold: 0.12 });

    document.querySelectorAll(".fade-in").forEach((el) => observer.observe(el));
  </script>

  <footer class="site-footer">
    <div class="container footer-inner">
      <nav class="footer-secondary">
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/takuya_asano_/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Instagram</a>
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@TakuyaAsanoDD" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">YouTube</a>
        <a href="https://open.spotify.com/artist/2EXtaUmvzUTnfXZx14NoDx" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Spotify</a>
        <a href="https://music.apple.com/jp/artist/%E6%B5%85%E9%87%8E%E8%A8%97%E7%9F%A2/1659347974" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Apple Music</a>
        <a href="https://takuyaasano.bandcamp.com/music" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Bandcamp</a>
      </nav>
      <p class="footer-copy">© Takuya Asano / 浅野託矢</p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
